<p>To install MOICE, you must have Office 2003 or 2007 Office system installed.</p>
<p>To install MOICE, you must have the Compatibility Pack for Word, Excel, and PowerPoint 2007 File Formats. The compatibility pack is available as a free download from the Microsoft Download Center:</p>
<p><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/download/details.aspx?familyid=941b3470-3ae9-4aee-8f43-c6bb74cd1466&amp;displaylang=en" data-linktype="external">Download the FileFormatConverters.exe package now</a></p>
