<p><a href="http://update.microsoft.com/microsoftupdate/v6/default.aspx?ln=en-us" data-linktype="external">http://update.microsoft.com/microsoftupdate/v6/default.aspx?ln=en-us</a></p>
<p>To enable MOICE, change the registered handler for the .ppt, .pot, and .pps file formats. The following table describes the command to enable or to disable MOICE for the .ppt, .pot, and .pps file formats:</p>
</li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Command to use to enable MOICE to be the registered handler</th>
<th>Command to use to disable MOICE as the registered handler</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
